{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":934,"text":"Here are some images of clusters of galaxies."},{"time":4268,"text":"They're exactly what they sound like."},{"time":6101,"text":"They are these huge collections of galaxies,"},{"time":8654,"text":"bound together by their mutual gravity."},{"time":10909,"text":"So most of the points that you see on the screen"},{"time":13571,"text":"are not individual stars,"},{"time":16100,"text":"but collections of stars, or galaxies."}]},{"cues":[{"time":18936,"text":"Now, by showing you some of these images,"},{"time":21267,"text":"I hope that you will quickly see that"},{"time":23014,"text":"galaxy clusters are these beautiful objects,"},{"time":25694,"text":"but more than that,"},{"time":27187,"text":"I think galaxy clusters are mysterious,"},{"time":29850,"text":"they are surprising,"},{"time":31403,"text":"and they're useful."},{"time":32820,"text":"Useful as the universe's most massive laboratories."},{"time":36351,"text":"And as laboratories, to describe galaxy clusters"},{"time":39987,"text":"is to describe the experiments"},{"time":41852,"text":"that you can do with them."}]},{"cues":[{"time":43405,"text":"And I think there are four major types,"},{"time":45685,"text":"and the first type that I want to describe"},{"time":48269,"text":"is probing the very big."},{"time":50488,"text":"So, how big?"},{"time":52183,"text":"Well, here is an image of a particular galaxy cluster."},{"time":56434,"text":"It is so massive that the light passing through it"},{"time":59403,"text":"is being bent, it's being distorted"},{"time":62018,"text":"by the extreme gravity of this cluster."},{"time":64527,"text":"And, in fact, if you look very carefully"},{"time":66331,"text":"you'll be able to see rings around this cluster."},{"time":69031,"text":"Now, to give you a number,"},{"time":70580,"text":"this particular galaxy cluster"},{"time":72363,"text":"has a mass of over one million billion suns."},{"time":76571,"text":"It's just mind-boggling how \nmassive these systems can get."},{"time":79884,"text":"But more than their mass,"},{"time":81385,"text":"they have this additional feature."},{"time":83359,"text":"They are essentially isolated systems,"},{"time":85703,"text":"so if we like, we can think of them"},{"time":87925,"text":"as a scaled-down version of the entire universe."},{"time":91195,"text":"And many of the questions that we might have"},{"time":93197,"text":"about the universe at large scales,"},{"time":95165,"text":"such as, how does gravity work?"},{"time":97080,"text":"might be answered by studying these systems."}]},{"cues":[{"time":100112,"text":"So that was very big."},{"time":101445,"text":"The second things is very hot."},{"time":103330,"text":"Okay, if I take an image of a galaxy cluster,"},{"time":106113,"text":"and I subtract away all of the starlight,"},{"time":109030,"text":"what I'm left with is this big, blue blob."},{"time":111825,"text":"This is in false color."},{"time":113310,"text":"It's actually X-ray light that we're seeing."},{"time":115659,"text":"And the question is, if it's not galaxies,"},{"time":118320,"text":"what is emitting this light?"},{"time":120519,"text":"The answer is hot gas,"},{"time":122419,"text":"million-degree gas --"},{"time":124242,"text":"in fact, it's plasma."},{"time":125899,"text":"And the reason why it's so hot"},{"time":127558,"text":"goes back to the previous slide."},{"time":129538,"text":"The extreme gravity of these systems"},{"time":132278,"text":"is accelerating particles of gas to great speeds,"},{"time":135320,"text":"and great speeds means great temperatures."},{"time":137902,"text":"So this is the main idea,"},{"time":139621,"text":"but science is a rough draft."},{"time":141987,"text":"There are many basic properties about this plasma"},{"time":144538,"text":"that still confuse us,"},{"time":146236,"text":"still puzzle us,"},{"time":147569,"text":"and still push our understanding"},{"time":149655,"text":"of the physics of the very hot."}]},{"cues":[{"time":151694,"text":"Third thing: probing the very small."},{"time":155121,"text":"Now, to explain this, I need to tell you"},{"time":157967,"text":"a very disturbing fact."},{"time":159987,"text":"Most of the universe's matter"},{"time":162777,"text":"is not made up of atoms."},{"time":164588,"text":"You were lied to."},{"time":166538,"text":"Most of it is made up of something \nvery, very mysterious,"},{"time":169665,"text":"which we call dark matter."},{"time":171787,"text":"Dark matter is something that \ndoesn't like to interact very much,"},{"time":175454,"text":"except through gravity,"},{"time":177122,"text":"and of course we would like to learn more about it."},{"time":178734,"text":"If you're a particle physicist,"},{"time":180277,"text":"you want to know what happens \nwhen we smash things together."},{"time":182786,"text":"And dark matter is no exception."}]},{"cues":[{"time":184776,"text":"Well, how do we do this?"},{"time":186436,"text":"To answer that question,"},{"time":187927,"text":"I'm going to have to ask another one,"},{"time":189320,"text":"which is, what happens when galaxy clusters collide?"},{"time":192486,"text":"Here is an image."},{"time":194796,"text":"Since galaxy clusters are representative"},{"time":197987,"text":"slices of the universe, scaled-down versions."},{"time":201111,"text":"They are mostly made up of dark matter,"},{"time":203234,"text":"and that's what you see in this bluish purple."},{"time":205787,"text":"The red represents the hot gas,"},{"time":207404,"text":"and, of course, you can see many galaxies."},{"time":209371,"text":"What's happened is a particle accelerator"},{"time":211736,"text":"at a huge, huge scale."},{"time":213627,"text":"And this is very important,"},{"time":215404,"text":"because what it means is that very, very small"},{"time":217287,"text":"effects that might be difficult to detect in the lab,"},{"time":220371,"text":"might be compounded and compounded"},{"time":222550,"text":"into something that we could \npossibly observe in nature."},{"time":226359,"text":"So, it's very funny."},{"time":227871,"text":"The reason why galaxy clusters"},{"time":229819,"text":"can teach us about dark matter,"},{"time":231485,"text":"the reason why galaxy clusters"},{"time":233235,"text":"can teach us about the physics of the very small,"},{"time":235788,"text":"is precisely because they are so very big."}]},{"cues":[{"time":238819,"text":"Fourth thing: the physics of the very strange."},{"time":242904,"text":"Certainly what I've said so far is crazy."},{"time":245954,"text":"Okay, if there's anything stranger"},{"time":248237,"text":"I think it has to be dark energy."},{"time":250654,"text":"If I throw a ball into the air,"},{"time":252371,"text":"I expect it to go up."},{"time":254169,"text":"What I don't expect is that it go up"},{"time":256293,"text":"at an ever-increasing rate."},{"time":258459,"text":"Similarly, cosmologists understand why"},{"time":261204,"text":"the universe is expanding."},{"time":262786,"text":"They don't understand why it's expanding"},{"time":264954,"text":"at an ever-increasing rate."},{"time":266892,"text":"They give the cause of this"},{"time":268570,"text":"accelerated expansion a name,"},{"time":270162,"text":"and they call it dark energy."},{"time":272046,"text":"And, again, we want to learn more about it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":274734,"text":"So, one particular question that we have is,"},{"time":277121,"text":"how does dark energy affect the universe"},{"time":279816,"text":"at the largest scales?"},{"time":281434,"text":"Depending on how strong it is,"},{"time":282893,"text":"maybe structure forms faster or slower."},{"time":286154,"text":"Well, the problem with the large-scale structure"},{"time":288703,"text":"of the universe is that it's horribly complicated."},{"time":291041,"text":"Here is a computer simulation."},{"time":293370,"text":"And we need a way to simplify it."},{"time":295498,"text":"Well, I like to think about this using an analogy."},{"time":299069,"text":"If I want to understand the sinking of the Titanic,"},{"time":301787,"text":"the most important thing to do"},{"time":303453,"text":"is not to model the little positions"},{"time":305234,"text":"of every single little piece of the boat that broke off."},{"time":308155,"text":"The most important thing to do is"},{"time":309820,"text":"to track the two biggest parts."},{"time":311821,"text":"Similarly, I can learn a lot about the universe"},{"time":315653,"text":"at the largest scales"},{"time":317120,"text":"by tracking its biggest pieces"},{"time":318871,"text":"and those biggest pieces are clusters of galaxies."}]},{"cues":[{"time":322862,"text":"So, as I come to a close,"},{"time":325818,"text":"you might feel slightly cheated."},{"time":327820,"text":"I mean, I began by talking about"},{"time":330070,"text":"how galaxy clusters are useful,"},{"time":332153,"text":"and I've given some reasons,"},{"time":333653,"text":"but what is their use really?"},{"time":336253,"text":"Well, to answer this,"},{"time":338370,"text":"I want to give you a quote by Henry Ford"},{"time":340986,"text":"when he was asked about cars."},{"time":342472,"text":"He had this to say:"},{"time":343831,"text":"\"If I had asked people what they wanted,"},{"time":346120,"text":"they would have said faster horses.\""},{"time":348903,"text":"Today, we as a society are faced"},{"time":351404,"text":"with many, many difficult problems."},{"time":353622,"text":"And the solutions to these \nproblems are not obvious."},{"time":357453,"text":"They are not faster horses."},{"time":359620,"text":"They will require an enormous amount of"},{"time":361862,"text":"scientific ingenuity."}]},{"cues":[{"time":363568,"text":"So, yes, we need to focus,"},{"time":365154,"text":"yes, we need to concentrate,"},{"time":366904,"text":"but we also need to remember that"},{"time":368870,"text":"innovation, ingenuity, inspiration --"},{"time":371705,"text":"these things come"},{"time":373037,"text":"when we broaden our field of vision"},{"time":374725,"text":"when we step back"},{"time":376065,"text":"when we zoom out."},{"time":377414,"text":"And I can't think of a better way to do this than"},{"time":379237,"text":"by studying the universe around us. Thanks."}]},{"cues":[{"time":382992,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}